WEBVTT

00:00:01.039 --> 00:00:04.047
I'd like to invite you to close your eyes.

00:00:06.063 --> 00:00:11.099
Imagine yourself standing
outside the front door of your home.

00:00:11.979 --> 00:00:14.768
I'd like you to notice
the color of the door,

00:00:14.792 --> 00:00:16.773
the material that it's made out of.

00:00:19.241 --> 00:00:25.036
Now visualize a pack
of overweight nudists on bicycles.

00:00:25.060 --> 00:00:26.491
(Laughter)

00:00:26.515 --> 00:00:29.189
They are competing
in a naked bicycle race,

00:00:29.213 --> 00:00:32.434
and they are headed straight
for your front door.